<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/28903860" target="_blank" data-id="3744570" data-za-element-name="Title">
为什么点赞手速过快会出现计赞 2 次？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/28903860/answer/42497619">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="12392320">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="42497619"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>2638</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
