<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/35936939" target="_blank" data-id="6581668" data-za-element-name="Title">
作为一个前端开发实习生，我这样做是不是特别不厚道？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/35936939/answer/65120573">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="21464034">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="65120573"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
