<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20285684" target="_blank" data-id="294544" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何应对网上的喷子？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20285684/answer/23308847">
