<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/19913979" target="_blank" data-id="145627" data-za-element-name="Title">
Java 和 JavaScript 是什么关系？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/19913979/answer/19080119">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="2808607">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="19080119"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>1982</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="count">1982</span>
<span class="label sr-only">赞同</span>
</button>
<button class="down ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label sr-only">反对</span>
</button>
</div>



<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">

<span class="summary-wrapper">
<span class="author-link-line">

<a class="author-link"
data-hovercard="p$t$muselover"
target="_blank" href="/people/muselover"
>缪斯的情人</a></span><span title="爆栈开发工程师 ，主要负责貌美如花" class="bio">
爆栈开发工程师 ，主要负责貌美如花
</span>
</span>
</div>

<div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="1982" data-async-voters="1">



<span class="voters text"><a href="#" class="more text"><span class="js-voteCount">1982</span>&nbsp;人赞同</a></span>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="145627" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="缪斯的情人" data-entry-url="/question/19913979/answer/19080119">

<textarea hidden class="content">&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/9c32a3e498cb5822f8fb3cd0d07b4a78_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;707&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;519&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;707&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/9c32a3e498cb5822f8fb3cd0d07b4a78_r.jpg&quot;&gt;</textarea>


<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix">
