<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/53686737" target="_blank" data-id="13694497" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何看待哔哩哔哩的 flv.js 作者月薪不到 5000 元？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/53686737/answer/136069239">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="49951100">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="136069239"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>1969</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="count">1969</span>
<span class="label sr-only">赞同</span>
