<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/50907897" target="_blank" data-id="12580600" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何入门微信小程序开发，有哪些学习资料？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/50907897/answer/128494332">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="46908609">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="128494332"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
