<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">

<span class="summary-wrapper">
<span class="author-link-line">

<a class="author-link"
data-hovercard="p$t$chu-xue-4"
target="_blank" href="/people/chu-xue-4"
>初雪</a></span><span title="测试小王子" class="bio">
测试小王子
</span>
</span>
</div>

<div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="1924" data-async-voters="1">



<span class="voters text"><a href="#" class="more text"><span class="js-voteCount">1924</span>&nbsp;人赞同</a></span>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="12580600" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="初雪" data-entry-url="/question/50907897/answer/128494332">

<textarea hidden class="content">&lt;b&gt;微信小程序正式公测，&lt;/b&gt;公测时间：11月3日夜；11月28日公布1月9日推出微信小程序；&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/portal.php%3Fmod%3Dview%26aid%3D911&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;张小龙全面阐述小程序，定档1月9日上线（附90分钟演讲全文） ...&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1月9日已经正式开放！&lt;br&gt;微信小程序展示及体验请看：&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//wxapp.dreawer.com&quot; class=&quot; external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;http://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;visible&quot;&gt;wxapp.dreawer.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;，小程序可在此链接内提交，方便展示；&lt;br&gt;前言：&lt;strong&gt;新人第一坑，跳坑指南：修改后，必须保存；ctrl+S；&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;特别提醒：&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1：下载开发者工具必须在如下工具地址下载，请勿从微信公众后台入口下载；如果你不小心下载安装了0.7.0版本的工具，请彻底删除后，重装如下地址的正确工具；&lt;br&gt;2:：如果安装后无法扫描登录，请在开发工具内代理位置查看是否设置了代理；假如正常使用中无法登陆，请稍后片刻或是删除重装工具，可能是官方出现了问题，&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;一：推荐地址集合：（初入门者请先看这里）&lt;br&gt;1：官方工具：&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//mp.weixin.qq.com/debug/wxadoc/dev/devtools/download.html%3Ft%3D1476434678461&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;https://mp.weixin.qq.com/debug/w ... tml?t=1476434678461&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;2：简易教程：&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//mp.weixin.qq.com/debug/wxadoc/dev/%3Ft%3D1476434677599&quot; class=&quot; external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;visible&quot;&gt;mp.weixin.qq.com/debug/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;wxadoc/dev/?t=1476434677599&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;3：设计指南：&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//mp.weixin.qq.com/debug/wxadoc/design/index.html&quot; class=&quot; external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;visible&quot;&gt;mp.weixin.qq.com/debug/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;wxadoc/design/index.html&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;4：&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/portal.php%3Fmod%3Dview%26aid%3D259&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序公测接入指南&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;5：微信支付：&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//pay.weixin.qq.com/wiki/doc/api/wxa/wxa_api.php%3Fchapter%3D1_1&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;【微信支付】微信小程序支付开发者文档&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/portal.php%3Fmod%3Dlist%26catid%3D19&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序支付&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;6：入门教程：&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/portal.php%3Fmod%3Dlist%26catid%3D7&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;新手教程&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;7：跳坑系列：&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dforumdisplay%26fid%3D2%26filter%3Dtype