er&quot;&gt;微信小程序学习用demo推荐：flex布局&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1254&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序控件练习demo：text、icon、progress、button、naviga&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1252&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序学习用demo：音乐播放控制&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1245&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序学习用demo：图片自适应&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1227&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序demo：拍照查字典；使用七牛云存储，ES6语法&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1225&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序学习用demo：豆瓣api，果壳api，知乎api&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1224&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序完整demo：jspapa：包含前后台nodejs+express+mongodb&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1216&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序demo：新闻阅读器：富文本解析，新闻API&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1215&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序学习用demo推荐：股票；形势，诊股&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1202&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序学习demo推荐：侧边栏滑动特效；四种特效&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1200&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序学习用demo推荐：滴滴作业：列表排序，位置&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.wxapp-union.com/forum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1197&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;微信小程序学习demo推荐：仿微信漂流瓶；使用leancloud&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;--------</textarea>


