<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/46943112" target="_blank" data-id="10991164" data-za-element-name="Title">
有哪些短小却令人惊叹的 JavaScript 代码？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/46943112/answer/103652342">
