<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="10991164" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="niaodan2b" data-entry-url="/question/46943112/answer/103652342">

<textarea hidden class="content">更正：经 &lt;a data-title=&quot;@PeakMuma&quot; data-editable=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;member_mention&quot; href=&quot;//www.zhihu.com/people/2a2548661b6844fbf5e7925c0a9b2159&quot; data-hash=&quot;2a2548661b6844fbf5e7925c0a9b2159&quot; data-hovercard=&quot;p$b$2a2548661b6844fbf5e7925c0a9b2159&quot;&gt;@PeakMuma&lt;/a&gt; 提醒，最早的出处应该是&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.weibo.com/1401880315/DgqKTmDoR%3Ffrom%3Dpage_1005051401880315_profile%26wvr%3D6%26mod%3Dweibotime%26type%3Dcomment%23_rnd1468810312550&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;JavaScript 错误处理的方式的正常姿势。[酷] 来自左耳朵耗子&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;345&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;440&quot; src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/c0f6f220f1e471e9b9a4b56bec257408_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;440&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/c0f6f220f1e471e9b9a4b56bec257408_r.jpg&quot;&gt;</textarea>


<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix">
<img data-rawheight="345" data-rawwidth="440" src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/c0f6f220f1e471e9b9a4b56bec257408_200x112.jpg" class="origin_image inline-img zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/c0f6f220f1e471e9b9a4b56bec257408_r.jpg">
