<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20303645" target="_blank" data-id="301743" data-za-element-name="Title">
为什么很多看起来不是很复杂的网站，比如 Facebook 需要大量顶尖高手来开发？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20303645/answer/15600019">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="1368057">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="15600019"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>1818</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
