<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/27085552" target="_blank" data-id="3017194" data-za-element-name="Title">
前端妹子跟我抱怨她们的页面加载很慢的时候，如何在她面前优雅地装逼？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/27085552/answer/35194131">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="9466036">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="35194131"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>1754</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
