<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/26025387" target="_blank" data-id="2593085" data-za-element-name="Title">
为什么 2014 年程序员薪资那么高？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/26025387/answer/31864662">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="8131423">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="31864662"> -->

